318
00:21:46,098 --> 00:21:47,969
- Protect them! - Protect them!

319
00:21:48,198 --> 00:21:49,338
Cancel the cruel schedules at once...

320
00:21:49,338 --> 00:21:50,368
It's Syaon!

321
00:21:50,368 --> 00:21:52,739
