372
00:25:54,979 --> 00:25:58,219
No. Just seeing you eat fills me up.

373
00:25:58,418 --> 00:25:59,688
Eat just one more.

374
00:25:59,688 --> 00:26:01,519
No. You eat more, Mom.

375
00:26:02,289 --> 00:26:03,928
Shall we play rock-paper-scissors and decide?

376
00:26:04,059 --> 00:26:05,088
