377
00:26:08,799 --> 00:26:10,029
- Rock-paper-scissors. - Rock-paper-scissors.

378
00:26:10,029 --> 00:26:11,128
It's three dollars.

379
00:26:11,128 --> 00:26:14,739
Add two servings of gimbap, and I'll pay for what they ate too.

380
00:26:14,799 --> 00:26:15,969
