504
00:34:53,618 --> 00:34:54,658
Yes.

505
00:34:54,658 --> 00:34:57,488
Withdraw your money and bring it back.

506
00:34:57,629 --> 00:34:58,689
Okay.

507
00:34:58,789 --> 00:35:00,899
I'll let your mom know.

508
00:35:00,899 --> 00:35:04,629
